--

CREATE TABLE question_versions (

    content_id integer,
    change_id integer,
    manual boolean NOT NULL,
    question_number integer,
    approval_date date,
    ministry_submit_date date,
    question_type character varying(1),
    response_type character varying(1),
    supplement_parent_id integer,
    sitting_time timestamp without time zone,
    ministry_id integer,
    response_text text,
    parliament_id integer,
    owner_id integer NOT NULL,
    language character varying(5) NOT NULL,
    short_name character varying(255) NOT NULL,
    full_name character varying(1024),
    body_text text,
    status character varying(48),
    status_date timestamp without time zone DEFAULT now() NOT NULL,
    registry_number integer,
    note text,
    receive_notification boolean,
    type character varying(30) NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT question_versions_question_type_check CHECK (((question_type)::text = ANY ((ARRAY['O'::character varying, 'P'::character varying])::text[]))),
    CONSTRAINT question_versions_response_type_check CHECK (((response_type)::text = ANY ((ARRAY['O'::character varying, 'W'::character varying])::text[])))
);

--
-- Name: users; Type: TABLE; Schema: public; Owner: undesa; Tablespace: 
--

CREATE TABLE users (
    user_id integer NOT NULL,
    login character varying(80),
    titles character varying(32),
    first_name character varying(256) NOT NULL,
    last_name character varying(256) NOT NULL,
    middle_name character varying(256),
    email character varying(512) NOT NULL,
    gender character varying(1),
    date_of_birth date,
    birth_country character varying(2),
    birth_nationality character varying(2),
    current_nationality character varying(2),
    uri character varying(120),
    date_of_death date,
    type_of_id character varying(1),
    national_id character varying(32),
    password character varying(36),
    salt character varying(24),
    description text,
    image bytea,
    active_p character varying(1),
    receive_notification boolean,
    language character varying(5) NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT users_active_p_check CHECK (((active_p)::text = ANY ((ARRAY['A'::character varying, 'I'::character varying, 'D'::character varying])::text[]))),
    CONSTRAINT users_gender_check CHECK (((gender)::text = ANY ((ARRAY['M'::character varying, 'F'::character varying])::text[])))
);


ALTER TABLE public.users OWNER TO undesa;

--
